name: The bird inside
description:
From the collection of "Inside: Light Sides"

 There is a singing bird in me
Which flies with the winds
He loves clouds
And is friends with stars
It can go up that much
That no one can reach him
My bird flies far and wide
Where no imagination can follow him
No thought can reach him
No mind can imagine it
I just need to close my eyes
He will spread his wings...
There is a singing bird inside...
